Trust the Journey…  Phoneix 🔥 rising 

I travel a lot, like almost every other weekend. However as I gathered my things to go on my next trip this one felt different… I texted my friend “As I’m on the plane and we are taking off it feels Like I’m on my way to my next chapter ….It’s kinda exciting but a little scary too “ 

I have so many things that I have grown through in my life that I desire to share, inspire and impact those that are divinely connected to me. My challenge has been how to organize those stories. Now I know a lot of it may be me in my perfection mode and fear. 

I’m trusting the process and the journey, allowing my mission to unfold. I’ve been to a lot of seminars, conferences, etc, etc.  I’ve learned so much and there was always one thing I felt I was missing.  I’m so grateful to say I’ve been blessed to be introduced to my next chapter in my story.

Life is like a roller coaster—filled with highs, lows, and unexpected twists. But it’s up to you to decide how your going to BE on this journey. 

 Remember how as kids, we couldn’t wait to get on that thrilling ride? It was all about the sheer joy and excitement!

But as adults, we get bogged down with fears and ‘what-ifs,’ forgetting the thrill that comes with the unknown. What if we took a page out of our younger selves’ book and lived in the moment? Seize the present 💝 like the gift it is, even if it’s a bit intimidating.

What if you chose to approach life with that child-like enthusiasm and you might discover that the ride isn’t just bearable, it’s exhilarating. It could be the reset you never knew you needed. 🌟 So buckle up, and enjoy the Journey💎
